ir\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":14361,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2013\/05\/20\/nifaq-enjoin-maruf-do-munkar\/","url_meta":{"origin":34955,"position":3},"title":"Hadith on Hypocrisy: Punishment for enjoining good, doing evil","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"May 20, 2013","format":false,"excerpt":"Usamah ibn Zayd reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \"A man will be brought on the Day of Resurrection and be cast into the Hellfire, and his intestines will pour forth in Hell. He will go around them as a donkey around a millstone.\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/sin-al-ithm\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":19776,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2014\/08\/22\/marry-loving-fertile\/","url_meta":{"origin":34955,"position":4},"title":"Hadith on Marriage: Marry the loving, fruitful to increase believers","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"August 22, 2014","format":false,"excerpt":"Anas ibn Malik reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, ordered us to get married and he strongly prohibited celibacy for us. The Prophet said, \u201cMarry the loving and fertile. Verily, I will have most followers among the prophets on the Day of Resurrection.\u201d Source: Musnad\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/righteousness-al-birr\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":24554,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2017\/03\/27\/sadaqah-people-all-deen-adyan\/","url_meta":{"orig